The paper proposes a method for applying self-attention to graph pooling, which is a technique commonly used in deep learning for structured data. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
